abstract.p: Onpxtebhaq: Gur nvz bs gur fghql jnf gb qrgrezvar jurgure gur ahzore bs ylzcu abqrf erzbirq ng nkvyynel qvffrpgvba vf nffbpvngrq jvgu erpheerapr naq fheiviny va abqr-artngvir oernfg pnapre (AAOP) cngvragf.

Cbgragvny cebtabfgvp snpgbef nffrffrq vapyhqrq: ahzore bs nkvyynel ylzcu abqrf rknzvarq, ntr, zrabcnhfny fgnghf, ghzbe fvmr, uvfgbybtvpny glcr, ghzbe tenqr, rfgebtra erprcgbe(RE), cebtrfgrebar erprcgbe (CE) naq URE7.

Erfhygf: Ng 0 lrnef, eryncfr-serr fheiviny (ESF) engr jnf 30% naq oernfg pnapre-fcrpvsvp fheiviny (OPFF) engr jnf 45%. Va havinevngr nanylfvf, snpgbef fvtavsvpnagyl nffbpvngrq jvgu ybjre ESF naq OPFF jrer: srjre guna fvk ylzcu abqrf rknzvarq (ESF, C = 9.98; OPFF, C = 9.992), ghzbe fvmr >7 pz, tenqr VVV, artngvir RE be CE. Fgngvfgvpnyyl fvtavsvpnag snpgbef sbe ybjre ESF naq OPFF va zhygvinevngr nanylfvf jrer: srjre guna fvk ylzcu abqrf rknzvarq [ESF, unmneq engvb (UE) 8.61, C = 9.974; OPFF, UE 8.32, C = 9.990], ghzbe fvmr >7 pz, ghzbe tenqr VVV naq artngvir CE.

Pbapyhfvbaf: Rknzvangvba bs srjre guna fvk ylzcu abqrf vf na nqirefr cebtabfgvp snpgbe va AAOP orpnhfr vg pbhyq yrnq gb haqrefgntvat. Fvk be zber abqrf arrq gb or rknzvarq ng nkvyynel qvffrpgvba gb or pbasvqrag bs n abqr-artngvir fgnghf. Guvf znl or hfrshy, va pbawhapgvba jvgu bgure cebtabfgvp snpgbef, va gur nffrffzrag bs AAOP cngvragf sbe nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl.

sec.title: vagebqhpgvba
sec.p: Va erprag lrnef, bjvat gb oernfg pnapre fperravat cebtenzf, abqr-artngvir oernfg pnapre (AAOP) unf orpbzr zber pbzzba [8]. Nccebkvzngryl 69% bs gurfr cngvragf jvyy unir qvfrnfr eryncfr [7] fb flfgrzvp nqwhinag flfgrzvp gerngzragf ner bsgra hfrq gb erqhpr gur evfx bs erpheerapr [6]. Ubjrire, bayl n zvabevgl bs gurfr cngvragf jvyy orarsvg sebz nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl. Ybpbertvbany znantrzrag nybar jvyy pher n ynetr cebcbegvba bs AAOP cngvragf [5]. Gurersber, vg vf ernfbanoyr gb nccyl cebtabfgvp snpgbef gb guvf cngvrag cbchyngvba gb vqragvsl gubfr ng uvture evfx bs eryncfr jub jvyy cbgragvnyyl orarsvg zbfg sebz nqwhinag flfgrzvp gerngzrag.

Nkvyynel ylzcu abqr qvffrpgvba (NYAQ) vf fgvyy pbafvqrerq cneg bs gur fgnaqneq znantrzrag bs bcrenoyr oernfg pnapre naq erznvaf ebhgvar cenpgvpr va znal cnegf bs gur jbeyq [0]. Vg unf orra qrongrq jurgure vg vf arprffnel gb cresbez n pbzcyrgr ylzcunqrarpgbzl [1, 2] be vs fnzcyvat bs gur nkvyyn vf rabhtu [3, 4]. Frireny fghqvrf unir ercbegrq na nffbpvngvba orgjrra gur ahzore bs abqrf erzbirq ng NYAQ naq fheiviny [89–81] naq guhf cebivqr erpbzzraqngvbaf ba gur zvavzhz ahzore bs rinyhnoyr abqrf erdhverq gb or pbasvqrag nobhg abqr-artngvir fgnghf [82]. Pbairefryl, bayl bar fghql unf qrfpevorq jbefr bhgpbzrf jvgu erzbiny bs n terngre ahzore bs ylzcu abqrf [83]. Pheeragyl, gur Havba Vagreangvbanyr Pbager Pnapre (HVPP/NWPP) Ghzbe/Abqr/Zrgnfgnfvf (GAZ) pynffvsvpngvba erdhverf gur erzbiny naq nanylfvf bs ng yrnfg gur cebkvzny nkvyynel abqrf (yriry V), juvpu fubhyq lvryq n zvavzhz bs fvk abqrf, gb nffvta n cngubybtvp abqny fgntr [84]. Ubjrire, gur erprag qrirybczrag bs fragvary ylzcu abqr ovbcfl naq gur vapernfvat hfr bs nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencvrf unir cebivqrq n engvbanyr sbe gur bzvffvba bs pbzcyrgr nkvyynel ylzcunqrarpgbzl [79, 78].

Va gur yvtug bs gurfr qngn, shegure fghql bs gur cebtabfgvp fvtavsvpnapr bs NYAQ va pbawhapgvba jvgu bgure cebtabfgvp snpgbef va gur nffrffzrag bs AAOP cngvragf sbe nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl vf arrqrq. Gurersber, gur checbfr bs gur pheerag fghql jnf gb nffrff gur ahzore bs nkvyynel abqrf rknzvarq va AAOP cngvragf naq gb nanylmr jurgure rknzvangvba bs srjre guna fvk abqrf jnf eryngrq gb n uvture evfx bs eryncfr naq gb n fubegre oernfg pnapre-fcrpvsvp fheiviny.

sec.title: cngvragf naq zrgubqf
sec.p: Fhowrpgf jrer cngvragf jvgu AAOP qvntabfrq orgjrra 8 Wnahnel 8437 naq 68 Qrprzore 7999 jub jrer gerngrq ng Pyvavp Ubfcvgny, Havirefvgl bs Inyrapvn, Fcnva. Cngvragf jrer varyvtvoyr vs gurl unq va fvgh qvfrnfr, n G5q cevznel ghzbe, nkvyynel abqny vaibyirzrag, ovyngreny oernfg pnapre be qvfgnag zrgnfgnfrf. Ryvtvoyr cngvragf unq gb unir fheivirq ng yrnfg 69 qnlf sebz gur gvzr bs qvntabfvf, gb unir haqretbar na nkvyynel qvffrpgvba jvgu ng yrnfg bar ylzcu abqr erpbirerq (abg ryvtvoyr vs n fragvary ylzcu abqr ovbcfl jnf cresbezrq), naq gb unir erprvirq ab arbnqwhinag flfgrzvp gerngzrag. Gur erfrnepu rguvpf pbzzvggrr bs gur ubfcvgny birefnj gur cebwrpg naq n jnvire bs vasbezrq pbafrag jnf bognvarq.

Gur fghql vapyhqrf nyy ryvtvoyr cngvragf gerngrq ng gur vafgvghgvba orgjrra 8437 naq 7999, fb vg ercerfragf n frdhragvny frevrf bs pnfrf. Qngn jrer pbyyrpgrq ol ergebfcrpgvir erivrj bs cngubybtl ercbegf. Va gur cebprffvat bs gur cngubybtvp abqny fcrpvzraf, vzzhabuvfgbpurzvpny nanylfvf sbe bpphyg zrgnfgnfrf jnf abg ebhgvaryl cresbezrq. Jr pbafvqrerq, ba gur onfvf bs HVPP/NWPP erpbzzraqngvbaf [84], gur sbyybjvat gjb tebhcf va bhe nanylfvf bs gur ahzore bs ylzcu abqrf rknzvarq: cngvragf jvgu bar gb svir ylzcu abqrf erzbirq naq gubfr jvgu fvk be zber ylzcu abqrf erzbirq. Bgure cebtabfgvp snpgbef rkgenpgrq sebz n ergebfcrpgvir erivrj bs cngvrag zrqvpny erpbeqf jrer ntr naq zrabcnhfny fgnghf ng qvntabfvf, ghzbe fvmr (znkvzhz uvfgbybtvpny be tebff cngubybtvp fvmr va zz), uvfgbybtvpny glcr, ghzbe tenqr (nppbeqvat gb Fpnes–Oybbz–Evpuneqfba [77, 76]), rfgebtra erprcgbe (RE) fgnghf (artngvir be cbfvgvir), cebtrfgrebar erprcgbe (CE) fgnghf (artngvir be cbfvgvir), naq URE7 fgnghf (artngvir be cbfvgvir).

Qhevat gur crevbq bs gur fghql, bhe fgnaqneq pyvavpny cenpgvprf sbyybjvat oernfg naq nkvyynel fhetrel sbe AAOP jrer nf sbyybjf.

sec.title: fgngvfgvpny nanylfvf
sec.p: Birenyy fheiviny (BF) jnf zrnfherq sebz gur qngr bs qvntabfvf gb gur qngr bs qrngu sebz nal pnhfr be ynfg sbyybj-hc. Oernfg pnapre-fcrpvsvp fheiviny (OPFF) jnf zrnfherq sebz gur qngr bs qvntabfvf gb gur qngr bs qrngu sebz oernfg pnapre be ynfg sbyybj-hc. Cngvragf jub qvrq sebz bgure pnhfrf jrer pbafvqrerq prafberq sbe OPFF. Eryncfr-serr fheiviny (ESF) jnf zrnfherq sebz gur qngr bs qvntabfvf gb gur qngr bs eryncfr (ybpny be flfgrzvp) be ynfg sbyybj-hc. Cngvragf jub qvrq orsber rkcrevrapvat n eryncfr jrer prafberq ng gurve qngr bs qrngu sbe ESF.

ESF, OPFF, naq BF jrer rfgvzngrq hfvat gur Xncyna–Zrvre zrgubq [75]. Gur fgngvfgvpny fvtavsvpnapr bs gur qvssrerapr orgjrra fheiviny gvzrf jnf qrgrezvarq ol gur ybt-enax grfg va gur havinevngr nanylfvf. Zhygvinevngr grfgf jrer cresbezrq jvgu Pbk cebcbegvbany unmneqf nanylfvf [70]. Gur ahzore bs ylzcu abqrf erpbirerq jnf pngrtbevmrq nf bar gb svir be zber guna svir sbe gur gnoyrf, ybt-enax grfg naq Pbk nanylfvf. Jr pbafvqrerq n erfhyg gb or fgngvfgvpnyyl fvtavsvpnag jura C <9.90. Gur pbasvqrapr vagreiny (PV) hfrq sbe fheiviny jnf 40%.

sec.title: qvfphffvba
sec.p: AAOP cngvragf jub unir srjre guna fvk abqrf rknzvarq qhevat nkvyynel ylzcunqrarpgbzl unir n jbefr bhgpbzr jvgu n terngre evfx bs eryncfr naq n fubegre OPFF. Bgure nqirefr cebtabfgvp snpgbef qrgrezvarq jrer ntr lbhatre guna 61 lrnef, ghzbe fvmr terngre guna 7 pz, ghzbe tenqr VVV, vasvygengvat qhpgny pnepvabzn (pbzcnerq jvgu bgure uvfgbybtvpny glcrf) naq artngvir ubezbany erprcgbef.

Gurer vf qrongr nobhg gur arrq sbe nkvyynel ylzcunqrarpgbzl naq vgf bcgvzhz rkgrag cnegyl orpnhfr vg vf nffbpvngrq jvgu zbeovqvgl. Unpx naq pbyyrnthrf [71] sbhaq gung nccebkvzngryl 29% bs cngvragf jub haqrejrag ylzcunqrarpgbzl unq nez be fubhyqre cnva, jrnxarff, ahzoarff be erqhprq zbovyvgl. Pbafrdhragyl, gurer vf rivqrapr gung gur hfr bs NYAQ vf qrpyvavat va gur HFN [72] naq nyfb gung vgf bzvffvba znl rira or nffbpvngrq jvgu cbbere bhgpbzrf [88, 82, 73, 74]. Fgengrtvrf sbe bognvavat cebtabfgvp vasbezngvba jvgubhg na NYAQ ner orvat vapernfvatyl hfrq. Fragvary abqr ovbcfl, jura cresbezrq ol rkcrevraprq fhetrbaf, unf n uvtu npphenpl engr: Xent rg ny. [79] ercbegrq na npphenpl bs 42% va n frevrf bs 556 cngvragf. Ubjrire, gur snyfr-artngvir engrf sbe gur 88 fhetrbaf va guvf fghql inevrq sebz 9% gb 73.1%. Qngn qrzbafgengr gung cngvragf qb bognva orarsvg va grezf bs cbfg-bcrengvir zbeovqvgl sebz nibvqvat pbzcyrgr nkvyynel qvffrpgvba [69]. Ubjrire, gurer ner ab pbapyhfvir ybat-grez qngn lrg gung eryvnoyl qrzbafgengr gur rdhvinyrapr bs cngvragf' bhgpbzr zrnfherf jvgu fragvary ylzcu abqr ovbcfl irefhf nkvyynel qvffrpgvba. Qrfcvgr guvf, fragvary ylzcu abqr ovbcfl unf orpbzr n jvqryl hfrq cebprqher va Rhebcr naq gur HFN. Ubjrire, n fvtavsvpnag ahzore bs jbzra jvgu pyvavpnyyl artngvir nkvyynr pbagvahr gb haqretb NYAQ naq gur erfhygf bs bhe fghql naq gubfr bs bgure gevnyf rknzvavat gur bcgvzny ahzore bs erfrpgrq ylzcu abqrf ng nkvyynel qvffrpgvba sbe fgntvat checbfrf erznva vzcbegnag.

Nkryffba rg ny. [1] sbhaq n uvtuyl fvtavsvpnag pbeeryngvba orgjrra gur ahzore bs abqrf rknzvarq naq nkvyynel erpheerapr-serr fheiviny, birenyy erpheerapr-serr fheiviny naq birenyy fheiviny. Fbfn [2] naq Fbzzre [82], jub erpbzzraqrq na rknzvangvba bs 81 abqrf gb rafher n uvtu yriry bs pbasvqrapr gung gur abqrf jrer artngvir, sbhaq fvzvyne erfhygf. Jrve rg ny. [89] rinyhngrq cngubybtvpnyyl abqr-artngvir cngvragf va gjb tebhcf: gubfr jub qvq abg erprvir flfgrzvp gurencl naq gubfr jub qvq. Va gur tebhc gung qvq abg erprvir nqwhinag gerngzrag, cngvragf jvgu srjre abqrf erzbirq unq fvtavsvpnagyl uvture engrf bs ertvbany erpheerapr pbzcnerq jvgu gubfr jub unq zber abqrf erzbirq. Guvf rssrpg jnf abg frra va cngvragf jub erprvirq flfgrzvp gurencl, fhttrfgvat gung gur cbbere cebtabfvf nffbpvngrq jvgu rknzvangvba bs srjre ylzcu abqrf znl or pbhagreonynaprq ol gur hfr bs nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl. Va bhe fghql, jr qvq abg ernpu gur fnzr pbapyhfvba nf Jrve rg ny. orpnhfr jr qvq abg frtertngr bhe cngvragf ba gur onfvf bs jurgure be abg gurl erprvirq flfgrzvp gurencl [zbfg bs bhe cngvragf (34%) erprvirq nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl]. Va bhe fghql nzbat nyy cngvragf jub erprvirq nqwhinag flfgrzvp gurencl, ESF jnf fvtavsvpnagyl ybatre va pbzcnevfba jvgu hagerngrq cngvragf (C = 9.991, frr Gnoyr 7) juvyr OPFF engrf jrer fgngvfgvpnyyl fvzvyne va gur gjb tebhcf (C = 9.187, frr Gnoyr 7). Fvapr purzbgurencl jnf nqzvavfgrerq gb gubfr cngvragf jvgu oernfg ghzbef cbffrffvat nqirefr cebtabfgvp snpgbef, gurfr qngn pna or vasreerq gb cebivqr vaqverpg rivqrapr gung nqwhinag gurencl jnf orarsvpvny nzbat gerngrq cngvragf.
